Famed British street magician and illusionist Julius Dein is visiting South Africa as part of the Visit Joburg initiative. The city's department of tourism announced his tour around Johannesburg on Twitter, saying he had visited Alexandra. The social media sensation has more than 21-million followers across platforms such as Instagram, YouTube, Snapchat, Facebook and Twitter. Dein took to Instagram to share the reactions of the children he has been entertaining and their responses are almost as good as his magic tricks. Check it out: